================================================================================
  PASSTO — DESIGN SYSTEM
  Handoff document for designers and web developers
  Last updated: 23 May 2026
================================================================================

PassTo is a primary-source-verified digital nursing license credential. It
lives in a nurse's Apple/Google Wallet and is shareable via a scannable link
or QR for real-time employer verification. Freemium — credential is free,
premium features layered on top.

Brand pillars:
  1. Verified  — Primary-source truth, not a photocopy
  2. Portable  — Lives in your wallet, not a filing cabinet
  3. Live      — Real-time, not a snapshot
  4. Yours     — Nurse-owned and nurse-controlled

Audience: US nurses — LPNs (~974K), travel nurses, agency nurses, new grads;
secondarily 5.2M RNs. 88% women, median age ~46. Tech-literate but time-poor.
The brand must be understood "by a nurse on hour 11 of a 12-hour shift."


