               Tracking -0.02em to -0.035em at heading scales
               H1–H4, wordmark, Pass name

  Body:        Public Sans  variable, weights 400/500/600
               Line-height 1.45 default
               Lede, body, captions

  Credential:  IBM Plex Mono  full weight range
