================================================================================

4px base scale. Always use flex/grid `gap` for sibling spacing — never
per-element margin.

  --pt-space-1     4px
  --pt-space-2     8px
  --pt-space-3    12px
  --pt-space-4    16px
  --pt-space-5    20px
  --pt-space-6    24px
  --pt-space-7    32px
  --pt-space-8    40px
  --pt-space-9    56px
  --pt-space-10   72px
  --pt-space-11   96px

RHYTHM
  - Marketing-site section-to-section: 96px top + bottom
  - Card-internal padding: 18–28px depending on density
  - Default page bg: paper-050. Elevated cards: paper-000.
  - Ink-900 used for premium / share-flow / footer surfaces. NEVER mid-tone gray.
  - No imagery as background in app surfaces.
  - No repeating patterns, no textures, no gradient meshes.
  - Subtle radial gradients only in hero, ≤10% opacity, e.g.
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(47,176,105,0.10), transparent 50%)


