  11. LOGO & WORDMARK
================================================================================

Assets in /assets/logo/:

  wordmark.svg            "PassTo" — light contexts; "To" rendered verified-600
  wordmark-on-dark.svg    "PassTo" — dark contexts; "To" rendered verified-400
