USAGE
  - The wordmark is "PassTo" — one word. Always.
  - In product UI, lead with the monogram. The wordmark appears in the header
    of marketing surfaces, the Pass head, and the App Store icon.
  - Minimum monogram size: 16×16. Minimum wordmark height: 14px.
  - Clearspace: half the cap height on all sides.
  - Never recolor outside the brand palette. Never apply effects, drop
    shadows, or gradients to the mark.


================================================================================
  12. ACCESSIBILITY
================================================================================

  - Hit targets: 44×44px minimum on touch surfaces.
  - Contrast: all text/foreground tokens meet WCAG AA at body sizes against
    their canonical backgrounds. Verify any new combination.
  - Focus-visible: always use the verified-green focus ring
    (--pt-shadow-focus). Never `outline: none` without a replacement.
  - Live region: the live-pulse should NOT auto-announce on screen readers
    every cycle — mark the status text as aria-live="polite" but the dot
    itself aria-hidden="true".
  - State color is never the only signal — pair with an icon, an eyebrow
    label, or a textual cue.


